metadata.name: Devil's morning
metadata.description:
-Ahhh, good morning Zizi, I slept so well, what time is it? 
-Meow 
-What? It's half past 11? I don't even have time for breakfast. Where's my stuff? God, what a mess, please fill the bathroom with blood, I'll take a shower and go get ready for the party. By the way, have you picked out a costume yet? 
-Meow
-Ohhh, you're so funny, are you serious? -Bat? I'm sure you'll be the best at the carnival. You know who's gonna be there, right? 
-Meow????
- Leelu's gonna be there. Don't tell me you don't care. Well, let's go get ready, my winged friend. We're in for an amazing adventure
-Oh Meow God!!!
